        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer452477604" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3612019503246601160">I loved it. West can make scary monsters and people to care about that are also scared of scary monster leading you to care about the people put in wonderfully scary spots. I started reading this book and I literally could not put it down. So just to sum it up this book is awesome, fun, scary, clever. This is a book that will not disappoint. <br/><br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


