<span id="freeTextContainer9336404495014261388">Spook House is the third installment in the Harmony, Indiana series by Michael West, it&apos;s a more of a monster novel that&apos;s filled with mythological creatures out of Lovecraft. I found the characters to be relatable and the monster very creepy, especially what they do to feed. It was nice to see characters from Cinema of Shadows featured in this book. I can&apos;t wait for the next book in the Harmony, Indiana series.</span>
  <span id="freeText9336404495014261388" style="display:none">Spook House is the third installment in the Harmony, Indiana series by Michael West, it's a more of a monster novel that's filled with mythological creatures out of Lovecraft. I found the characters to be relatable and the monster very creepy, especially what they do to feed. It was nice to see characters from Cinema of Shadows featured in this book. I can't wait for the next book in the Harmony, Indiana series.</span>
